Adding Python to Windows Path
        (1) Windows + Pause|Break to access system
        (2) Advanced System Settings
        (3) Environment Variables
        (4) Select Path under System variables then Edit
        (5) New: add C:\Program Files (x86)\Python35-32

Upgrading Pip
        (1) Open Windows CMD with Administrator Privileges
        (2) Python -m pip install --upgrade pip
        
Installing Python Wheel (XlsxWriter) with Pip
        (1) Open Windows CMD
        (2) Python -m pip install C:\Users\wesle\Documents\Python\XlsxWriter-0.8.5-py2.py3-none-any.whl
